{
  "stem": "12255.2",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.5,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well now, another aspect of the illegal immigration-- we call it Aliyah Bet-- was carried out by my friend-- my dear friend Abraham, who, as I said, spoke French fluently as well as German and Yiddish.",
      "word_count": 36
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And he wasn't too bad in English.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he was quite a modern rabbi.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we received-- some nut in England got the idea of providing the chaplains with a big vehicle, tremendous sort of caravan type of vehicle, so that the chaplain could take his synagogue with him.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Well, I had a-- I had a little ark made for me in the work-- in the army workshop.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "It was a small Sefer Torah.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And I had a 1,500 weight lor-- van.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And that was quite enough.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they sent these great big, lumbering things.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 58,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And nobody knew what to do with them.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By this time, Abraham had been adopted by the Joint, the American Joint Distribution Committee, which had an office in Brunswick, which is more near the border-- near the British zone bordered with, with the, with the Russian zone.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And in Brunswick, there was also a very, very fine Jewish, Jewish kind of [INAUDIBLE], a Jewish what would you call it?",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 59,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Army assistance group?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It was a-- not a hotel.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 60,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "A club.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, a club.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "OK.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 61,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Sorry, OK.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "A Jewish club open to everybody during the week, but closed on Friday night and Saturday, when we held Jewish services there, you see.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We had-- always had a nice Friday night supper and so on and so forth.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And the, the Joint had a brunch there as well.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they adopted Abraham, and he adopted one of these vans, which nobody had any use for.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
